# Optional agent credentials — the practice loop itself needs NO secrets.
#
# In GitHub Codespaces, prefer Codespaces secrets (Settings → Codespaces →
# Secrets) over a local file; the devcontainer declares these names so the
# create screen offers them. Locally, export them in your shell — the justfile
# deliberately does not auto-load dotenv files (`set dotenv-load := false`).
#
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=    # Claude Code as interviewer (alt: run `claude` and log in)
# OPENAI_API_KEY=       # OpenAI Codex as interviewer (alt: `codex login --device-auth`)
